{"tid":2257782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"街頭抗爭嘅歷史使命係咪已經完成咗？","createTime":"2020-10-25T13:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T05:53:35.000Z","uid":99725,"like":133,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"409430cc3d289cf76c282b97704f584451164195","tid":2257782,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:09:06.000Z","msg":"先唔好提個運動係咪冷卻咗<br />\n面對着肺炎，國安法，限聚令等等嘅因素，無可否認會令好多人卻步。<br />\n再加上而家國際戰線打得如火如荼，BNO及其他難民方案如箭在弦，相信有很多有錢)人都會選擇移民至其他地方。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢啲因素影響之下，街頭抗爭仲有冇存在嘅必要？我認為呢個係值得大家去探討。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=有存在嘅必要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=專心國際戰線，唔會再出去<br />\n<br />\n無論你投咩都好，希望你留言講埋原因"},{"pid":"2b3eace94dd201a9db9f9c732affefbba53a8621","tid":2257782,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:09:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"911e5f02beef02687e17a66e64883fddfab9db23","tid":2257782,"uid":99725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:10:03.000Z","msg":"認真po冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b371be61fc282ad0d79537a4d8322fc01377ae1d","tid":2257782,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:10:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7549027e99bd339dfda2486ed48bcb2d0a4eee5c","tid":2257782,"uid":207702,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:11:11.000Z","msg":"勇武抗爭 唯一出路"},{"pid":"74962f70824a6e808c66b9d3532cdb08faf2da16","tid":2257782,"uid":258903,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:11:22.000Z","msg":"待機而動<br />\n暫時氣氛要chok番起<br />\n的確事倍功半<br />\n等待中先打國際線"},{"pid":"5ba386cbeeefc9dc4ad6d9ec43b67063a6843e40","tid":2257782,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:11:25.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"150882c8d9a2e247540a44b243b71a729920ecfc","tid":2257782,"uid":99725,"like":3,"dislike":6,"sc